  <div class="container-right">
    <div align="left">
      <p>Using color to only differenciate a link from the text is inaccessible for colorblind users.</p>
      <p>In the following example, the chapter 1 and last paragraph are links, without underline. It's difficult, if not impossible to see the difference between the text and the links available.</p>
      <p>Learn more: <a href="https://axesslab.com/colorblind-accessibility-web-fail-success-cases/" target="_blank"
          rel="noopener">Render links accessible</a></p>
    </div>
